        Summary:
        Heartland Commerce is seeking a Senior Data Scientist.
        Heartland Commerce does cool things like build next generation POS systems for some of the biggest casual dining and quick service restaurants in the U.S. You'll have the opportunity to work with an organization that has a "startup" feel but the stability of a Fortune 1000 company. We work hard but have fun too! We have a casual dress code and our new office in the Ballantyne area of Charlotte has an open floor plan, fresh design, and even a lounge room where you can take a break and play some video games!
        If this sounds like a place for you, continue reading and apply today!
        Job Details:
